title: Innaway - Innaway
description:
Debut album from this California act that play an ambient-influence style of rock that brings together influences like Led Zeppelin and Pink Floyd to Air and Tortoise. An expansive, dynamic record produced and engineered by John McEntire.

* Jim Schwartz - vocals/keyboards/guitar
* Barry Fader - guitar/backup vocals
* Reid Black - keyboards/guitar
* Darrick Rasmussen - bass
* Gabe Palmer - drums
* Maori Konishi - keyboards/saxophone (2001-2002)

Track list:
1. Threat Hawk
2. The Strings of North Egg
3. Tiny Brains
4. Rise
5. Fall
6. Follow Moon
7. Post FM
8. Golden
9. Stolen Days
10. George Walker on Water

Enjoy.
